---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="sf frens zines">
  <main>
    <h1>sf frens zines</h1>
    <p>
      The theme for zine 5 is "shenanigan(s)". Send us your submissions using 
      <a href="https://forms.gle/HcWhivR7HSzK69tH7">this form</a>! Submissions are open until May 24, 2026.
    </p>
    <br>
    <p>
      zine, n. "a small-circulation self-published work of original or
      appropriated texts and images" — <a
        href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zine">Wikipedia</a
      >
    </p>
    <p>
      We’re sf frens, a supportive community for creative growth based in San
      Francisco. Our main production is our biannual zine, where we collect
      short stories, poetry, art, and weirder things (crosswords? weather data
      visualizations? maps?). Each zine is accompanied by a launch party, which
      is also an open mic.
    </p>

    <p>
      Follow us on <a href="https://www.instagram.com/sf_frens/">Instagram</a> for
      updates.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/issue1">Edition 01</a></li>
      <li><a href="/issue2">Edition 02</a></li>
      <li><a href="/issue3">Edition 03</a></li>
      <li><a href="/issue4">Edition 04</a></li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://forms.gle/qoe1t5rvvsbk7RBq7">Request</a> reprints
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://forms.gle/ZmWT4pNB8EmpwQiN9">Sign up</a> to submit for future
        issues
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="mailto:inquiries@sf-frens.org">Email us</a> for general inquiries
      </li>
    </ul>

    <style>
      h1 {
        font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        -webkit-text-stroke: 0;
        display: inline-block;
        position: relative;
        padding-bottom: 14px;
      }

      h1::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0;
        left: -4px;
        right: -4px;
        height: 14px;
        background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 300 14' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cpath d='M 2,9 C 30,3 60,13 90,7 C 120,1 150,12 180,7 C 210,2 240,11 298,8' stroke='white' stroke-width='3' fill='none' stroke-linecap='round'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        background-size: 100% 100%;
      }

      ul {
        list-style: lower-greek;
      }

      form {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 8px;
      }
    </style>
  </main>
</Layout>
